item.title: Rocket League
item.description:
Welcome to season three, episode 119 of Digital Dissection: Pop Culture Nerdity! Today, Mark and Joe do a retro review of the 2015 game Rocket League! This game continues to keep players in front of screens today with over 91 million active players! Download this episode to hear about what keeps people coming back to rocket powered cars playing soccer!

Music by Joystock: ⁠https://www.joystock... Feed: https://anchor.fm/s/5337b40c/podcast/rss
